Corporate Associate, Top Tier Firm, 4+PQE, Dubai or Abu Dhabi
Corporate Associate, Top Tier Firm, 4+PQE, Dubai or Abu Dhabi
Location:  --Abu Dhabi
This market leading, global law firm is seeking a strong mid/senior level corporate lawyer to join them in Dubai or Abu Dhabi, working on high profile, high quality deals. You will have at least 4 years’ corporate experience from a top tier law firm, a track record of acting as lead associate on transactions and have significant M&A and/or ECM exposure. It is essential that you have first class legal ability coupled with a practical commercial approach and excellent drafting and communication skills. You must also have exceptional results throughout your academic history. You should demonstrate strong communication and analytical skills and a high level of commercial awareness.
The successful candidate will handle a variety of work, including public and private M&A, equity capital markets transactions across the Middle East. You will be expected to take responsibility for significant elements of a transaction. Emerging market experience would be valued, but is not a prerequisite.
For further details, candidates fulfilling the above criteria are invited to send their CV in complete confidence to
